{"tid":441320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（急救）有無郵差叔叔係到？","createTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T20:41:24.000Z","uid":24590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1192a2de2b0f4fe7c36309982c1d0bfe6ea0306","tid":441320,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日喺小巴唔見咗銀包<br />\n個銀包有我爸爸張身分證<br />\n而佢近排有事入咗醫院 可以出院補領的機率好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日撞返個司機<br />\n佢話啲乘客拎咗，揼落綠色嘅郵筒<br />\n已知係荃灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問如果你哋喺郵筒執到銀包會放喺度幾日定係上繳去總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者我要去邊或者打邊個電話先搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecfb3bb83d5b005e1e3ca8fdab4b689c94276f3","tid":441320,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8e829c386c8f0118efe0edfb23d436f925efa81","tid":441320,"uid":24590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de87539d713ca7360d6c98224a504fb120b0ccca","tid":441320,"uid":144943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9de77446aa1b0fe1277c03575993ede7151880c","tid":441320,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd3a891157153ca5eb1d43fef76d6af3b998d8e4","tid":441320,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"重力一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3741deaaea29509ea147b94aa5907505f